{"tid":900803,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"瞞住職場其他人，同一個同事曖昧緊，個感覺真係好正","createTime":"2018-11-13T13:58:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-13T15:01:36.000Z","uid":2702,"like":6,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"62f4032731dfe4c906abaf4516e7314a256bf94c","tid":900803,"uid":2702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T13:58:28.000Z","msg":"今日仲有個已婚女同事問我鐘意咩女仔，話要幫我介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我話唔洗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢就話我係咪唔想拍拖，鐘意一個人自由自在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n珠不知我就暗地裹同另一個女同事互flirt<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n曖昧真係好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：溝緊個40路，所以無人會懷疑我同佢有野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f426aba7714d9221c4422af37e34d926618fd71","tid":900803,"uid":56940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T13:59:34.000Z","msg":"重口味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc3980c2c6be776b92c4f38e32488dfcb9cdb889","tid":900803,"uid":115949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T14:00:26.000Z","msg":"磨牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77115ecd8b52f07ad5d91dd0fccea9711bef2966","tid":900803,"uid":170867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T14:11:49.000Z","msg":"煲老嘔 勁"},{"pid":"565ca2f68e449821dc396748d94215dc2156abc8","tid":900803,"uid":2702,"like":8,"dislike":5,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T14:23:37.000Z","msg":"今日我讚佢著得可愛<br />\n佢勁開心<br />\n我再話：呀邊個邊個（另一個女同事）今日都著得好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢即刻嬲左（勁可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ），然後係我耳邊話：呀邊個今日好靚仔<br />\n<br />\n我真心估唔到佢會咁激番我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即刻呆左，連野都講唔到：下⋯你⋯下⋯<br />\n<br />\n之後有個男同事問我咩事，我即刻扮無野，扯開話題<br />\n佢之後即刻偷望我同個男同事，好似好驚比佢識穿咁<br />\n<br />\n曖昧真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我戀愛了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然佢大我20年，但你地根本唔知佢有幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59d23eb1aa808a41df6e296dc7daa847880f4113","tid":900803,"uid":2702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T14:41:08.000Z","msg":"推比全世界知我墜入愛河<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d46c3989aef8a59586e51ea8094c7fbfce16bf2","tid":900803,"uid":55583,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T14:43:41.000Z","msg":"全世界都知你同洗廁所個阿姐有路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係你地以為冇人知咋"},{"pid":"1dead2c6568f37e4220803e86dc8b1a8e3e5b90f","tid":900803,"uid":28450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T15:01:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c46c7c8b3e1f24ead20380e87c2003eab11418c3","tid":900803,"uid":2702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d46c3989aef8a59586e51ea8094c7fbfce16bf2","tid":900803,"uid":55583,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T14:43:41.000Z","msg":"全世界都知你同洗廁所個阿姐有路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係你地以為冇人知咋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T15:01:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}